                        h2#sub-title.mx-auto.mt-4.mb-4 AI-driven materials discovery for sustainable industries
                    .col-12.text-center.mb-xs-5.mb-lg-0
                        p.mission-text The chemical industry must innovate with more sustainable materials and chemical processes. We have developed a generative AI platform that helps discover new catalysts that optimize for the right chemical reactions, all while factoring in physicochemical and manufacturing constraints.
